title: 10 Takeaways from Week 14
itunes:title: 10 Takeaways from Week 14
description:
Daniel Jeremiah, Rhett Lewis & Bucky Brooks recap Week 14 of the NFL season, including the Rams big win over the Seahawks (:54), Drew Lock's impressive performance (3:24), how the Browns lost even though they won against the Bengals (6:17), evaluating the Patriots' poor offense in Week 14 (10:35), a look at how Titans' QB Ryan Tannehill is on fire (14:03), why the Ravens' defense is dangerous (18:24), a discussion on the Colts flopping against the Buccaneers (23:19), analyzing how the Packers are best when RB Aaron Jones is the focal point (27:10), a deep dive into Chargers' RB Austin Ekeler's huge day (30:15) and to wrap up the show, explaining why 49ers' QB Jimmy Garoppolo is a winner (34:10).
